what we're gonna be showing
you is just a rough idea.

626
00:38:21,648 --> 00:38:26,643
Oh! Uh, wait.
No, this is--this is not the right file.

627
00:38:26,655 --> 00:38:29,520
Um, just one sec--one second.

628
00:38:29,537 --> 00:38:31,143
This is it.

629
00:38:31,155 --> 00:38:37,500
Um... in order to show the
softer side of Fabia Cosmetics,

630
00:38:37,515 --> 00:38:41,021
we're going to use the concept
of mothers and daughters,

631
00:38:41,035 --> 00:38:44,690
focusing on the small,
special moments that--

632
00:38:44,707 --> 00:38:47,113
that are usually
taken for granted,

633
00:38:47,308 --> 00:38:52,391
the theme being, "it's not the big
events... but the little moments"
that matter.

634
00:38:52,405 --> 00:38:54,653
I just had a daughter.

635
00:38:54,668 --> 00:38:57,301
I do none of those things...

636
00:38:57,417 --> 00:38:59,713
but I can understand.

637
00:39:00,228 --> 00:39:04,290
What makes you think this is
going to appeal to my customers?

638
