in fact, there's been tremendous
brand loyalty since you've launched,

641
00:39:21,205 --> 00:39:23,521
which means that the
people who were teenagers

642
00:39:23,538 --> 00:39:25,233
when they began
using your cosmetics,

643
00:39:25,248 --> 00:39:28,561
well, now, like you,
they are...

644
00:39:28,577 --> 00:39:30,932
beginning to settle down
and have children--

645
00:39:30,948 --> 00:39:34,411
um, 58% to be exact.

646
00:39:34,845 --> 00:39:37,113
And you could do this in time?

647
00:39:37,126 --> 00:39:38,712
Of course.

648
00:39:38,725 --> 00:39:43,001
Uh, did you want to approve the, uh,
uh, models and images beforehand?

649
00:39:43,016 --> 00:39:46,812
Nah. Just make sure
it's not too sappy.

650
00:39:46,827 --> 00:39:51,163
Do a picture where they're pulling
their hair or biting each other.

651
00:39:51,227 --> 00:39:52,920
So that's nice.

652
00:39:52,937 --> 00:39:54,733
Now I go.

653
00:40:00,436 --> 00:40:01,820
Good work.

654
00:40:01,835 --> 00:40:06,681
- Oh, the idea was actually--
- His best one, don't you think?

655
00:40:09,555 --> 00:40:11,122
Indeed.

656
00:40:11,135 --> 00:40:13,291
Welcome back, boss.

657
00:40:13,396 --> 00:40:14,960
Marc.

658
00:40:28,436 --> 00:40:31,282
I'm very unhappy.

659
00:40:31,297 --> 00:40:33,243
It's a setback.

660
00:40:33,258 --> 00:40:35,261
But it's just a matter of time.

661
00:40:35,278 --> 00:40:36,942
Once he's out of the picture,

662
00:40:36,957 --> 00:40:39,782
the company will be
ours for the taking.

663
00:40:39,796 --> 00:40:41,982
Considering the way
everything's played out,

664
00:40:41,997 --> 00:40:47,023
